<p><small><i>This is an edition of </i>The Atlantic<i> Daily, a newsletter that guides you through the biggest stories of the day, helps you discover new ideas, and recommends the best in culture. </i></small><a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/newsletters/sign-up/atlantic-daily/?utm_source=feed"><i><small>Sign up for it here.</small></i></a></p><p>This week, I talked to wildlife experts about my most pressing springtime animal questions. But first, here are three stories from <i>The Atlantic</i>:</p><ul>
